Cafe

Americano $3.90

An Americano is made by adding hot water to a shot of espresso. This results in a coffee that is similar in strength to a regular drip coffee, but with a richer and more intense flavor.

Espresso $3.00

A classic Italian-style coffee made by forcing hot water through finely-ground coffee beans. This strong and bold coffee is served in a small cup and can be enjoyed on its own or used as the base for other coffee drinks.

Cappuccino $4.00

Similar to a latte, a cappuccino is made with a shot of espresso and steamed milk. However, it has a thicker layer of foam on top, giving it a light and airy texture. It is typically served in a small cup and can be enjoyed as a morning pick-me-up or a mid-day treat.

Latte $4.50

A latte is made by combining a shot of espresso with steamed milk and a small layer of foam on top. This creamy and smooth coffee has a mild and slightly sweet taste that is perfect for those who prefer a milder coffee flavor.

Food

Grilled Salmon $16.90

Fresh, wild-caught salmon grilled to perfection and served with a side of roasted vegetables.

Chicken Alfredo $14.99

Grilled chicken breast served on a bed of fettuccine pasta tossed in a creamy Alfredo sauce with a side of garlic bread.

Classic Cheeseburger $12.99

Juicy beef patty cooked to order and topped with melted cheddar cheese, lettuce, tomato, onion, and a special sauce. Served with fries.

Margherita Pizza $13.99

Classic Neapolitan pizza topped with San Marzano tomatoes, fresh mozzarella, and basil leaves.

Vegan Buddha Bowl $15.99

A mix of hearty quinoa, roasted sweet potatoes, chickpeas, and fresh greens topped with a flavorful tahini dressing.

Steak Frites $22.99

A juicy cut of grilled sirloin steak served with a generous portion of crispy french fries. Perfect for meat-lovers, this classic dish is sure to satisfy any appetite.

Beef and Broccoli Stir-Fry $17.99

Thinly sliced beef stir-fried with broccoli, carrots, and onions in a savory soy sauce. Served over a bed of fluffy white rice.

Chicken Parmesan $17.95

Breaded chicken breast topped with marinara sauce, mozzarella, and Parmesan cheese, served with a side of spaghetti.

Dessert

Chocolate Cake $6.99

Moist layers of chocolate cake with rich chocolate frosting. Perfect for chocolate lovers!

Apple Pie $5.99

A classic dessert made with fresh, juicy apples and a flaky crust. Served with a dollop of whipped cream.

Cheesecake $7.99

Creamy and decadent, our cheesecake is made with a graham cracker crust and topped with your choice of fruit compote.

Ice Cream Sundae $4.99

Scoops of vanilla ice cream topped with hot fudge, whipped cream, and a cherry. A sweet and simple treat for any occasion.

Entrée

Mango Lassi $4.00

A popular Indian drink made with yogurt, mango puree, and spices. Served chilled, this creamy beverage is a perfect balance of sweet and tangy flavors.

Lemonade $2.50

A classic summer drink made with freshly squeezed lemon juice, sugar, and water. Refreshing and tart, this drink is perfect for a hot day.

Green tea $3.00

A refreshing beverage made from steeped green tea leaves. Served hot or iced, this beverage is known for its antioxidants and health benefits.
